I have a BA-4 under the front of the bus hanging on the old AC
evaporator (or is it condenser)brackets,  I then use the old AC fan
under the dash to blow air down to the intakes of the BA-4 which then
outputs into the old air duct just behind the front axles (cut off and
capped behind)

have lots of heat,
defrost works fantastic
don't have rear seats so not sure how much gets back there

Bob

